data.description: Enjoy country living on this beautiful secluded 5-acre property! This 3BR 2-1/2BA 1564 Sq. ft. Home has a very comfortable & charming floor plan that includes an enclosed sunroom.  5 acres of usable land that is fenced and has a great shop for all your hobbies. Enjoy the Del Rio HOA (small yearly fee) that includes shared 6 acres of North Umpqua riverfront, 100+ riding trails, and hiking trails!
